This is your new Play application
=====================================

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `play dist`.

How to install Play Framework in Ubuntu:
http://www.red-geek.com.ar/todo-java/instalar-el-framework-play-en-ubuntu.php

How to create a first project with Play Framework:
http://www.red-geek.com.ar/todo-java/crear-un-proyecto-en-play-framework.php

In this link you can see this simple example in the cloud
http://limitless-ravine-6109.herokuapp.com
If you see an error in this link it is because this example was deployed in a free account in Heroku, 
you could try later
